    <a href="http://blog.crisp.se/henrikkniberg/2009/06/26/1246053060000.html#comment1246367635835" title="http://blog.crisp.se/henrikkniberg/2009/06/26/1246053060000.html#comment1246367635835">#</a>
  </div>

  <div class="responseBody">
    Is the change in dev limit from 2 to 3 intended to signify anything, other than the limits can change?

I generally think that <em>reducing</em> the limits is a sign of improvement as the team achieves better flow
  </div>

</div>

